{"tid":778282,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人又話做科文好游...","createTime":"2018-08-13T14:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T07:22:41.000Z","uid":200608,"like":32,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"221cbc3cf632435f531bd3c99da0eece768a4e45","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"點解我會咁撚忙...<br />\n我入左行先得幾個月就放我一個睇住個盤<br />\n對住風火水電煤咁多個行頭...<br />\n是否正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n以前係大樓做藍領(當然係𡃁仔啦)果陣<br />\n會有墨斗王彈晒墨比自己做<br />\n依家轉左做裝修盤<br />\n冇墨斗王<br />\n我依個科文就要跟住𢭃木佬彈墨<br />\n跟下現場啲數同圖紙有冇出入...我都明係職責一部份黎<br />\n但得我一個科文<br />\n跟得墨黎<br />\n地盤其他野真係分唔到身去理<br />\n如果去左理其他野 <br />\n例如有其他師傅問野走左去答<br />\n返到黎又未必跟得返啲墨<br />\n再唔係就係依邊彈緊墨<br />\n第邊有師傅已經埋位做緊野跟住做錯<br />\n最後大佬黎到就問我點解師傅會做錯呀<br />\n你冇睇住啲師傅做野嫁咩？<br />\n又或者同客開會我大佬無端端指住條墨問我依到點解會改左<br />\n又或者個客問我野<br />\n我大佬唔幫口不特止仲問我更加多問題<br />\n跟住我就一臉茫然...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同啲師傅夾野<br />\n佢地會問我啲野點安裝<br />\n依part我又唔係好明<br />\n以前我做大樓<br />\n未見過啲師傅會問返管工轉頭啲野點做<br />\n係咪因為大樓同裝修既完成品性質不同？<br />\n佢地又會問我啲野點收口<br />\n依個時候我真係收口 唔識答人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己真係好廢<br />\n乜都唔識<br />\n好想逃走<br />\n師傅問自己野<br />\n冇一樣可以確實答到人<br />\n真係好驚一陣答錯人<br />\n啲野做錯左又要改<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀<br />\n我先入行幾個月<br />\n你就丟我一個係地盤自生自滅<br />\n我真係跟唔黎呀<br />\n好擔心啲野有甩漏<br />\n唔知埋下左幾多個地雷比自己踩<br />\n日日都好不安<br />\n每日都諗緊幾時辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋想請教下咁多位ching<br />\n科文駛唔駛對客？<br />\n定係PM既職責黎？<br />\n我有時要自己同客夾<br />\n<br />\n我想問下咁多位ching<br />\n我面對緊困難不安係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 科文必經 根本就係你個人廢 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你公司分工安排、培訓有問題 遞信啦"},{"pid":"57015bd3d095bdf05f988cf28a1d9dd68c26a00f","tid":778282,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"點解你腦世會請你? 你無料又去見工?"},{"pid":"4376ef527b5d587f926537a64967c7a89cf62080","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57015bd3d095bdf05f988cf28a1d9dd68c26a00f","tid":778282,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"點解你腦世會請你? 你無料又去見工?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"佢話就係睇中我係白紙<br />\n話啲有經驗既唔聽人講野<br />\n同埋會走精面"},{"pid":"e58b7e3370c1f5e75f67a213c1dbe363b2070d4d","tid":778282,"uid":4355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:49:53.000Z","msg":"起樓同裝修project sum都唔同啦"},{"pid":"f4852b80b2b521402d2ab6955993720e1214010c","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57015bd3d095bdf05f988cf28a1d9dd68c26a00f","tid":778282,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"點解你腦世會請你? 你無料又去見工?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"同埋搵餐晏仔食姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7eaea2fb5f9e4d35f3c272f29a337fa6f9885ad","tid":778282,"uid":75768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"屌番個大佬轉頭，話唔夠人手，師傅又問野，彈墨又要跟，分身咩。"},{"pid":"938afaadd738afcabced9d7702b14c7433230fe2","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7eaea2fb5f9e4d35f3c272f29a337fa6f9885ad","tid":778282,"uid":75768,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"屌番個大佬轉頭，話唔夠人手，師傅又問野，彈墨又要跟，分身咩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"始終係新仔<br />\n未摸得清一個正常科文既能力值係應該去到邊<br />\n可能原來個個科文都識分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以同一時間handle到咁多野<br />\n不過見到巴打你咁講我安心啲<br />\n原來真係唔合理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173174733cb0ea39f98fbe5396ed9397af8586ba","tid":778282,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"白紙一張最忌無人帶無人教<br />\n你估真係屌下就識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d4e6495540f785be1d76fef4ced22b3f24bed4","tid":778282,"uid":30701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"白紙坐正科文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f3e9a21582bb973154c6365f60bc1709e90c84","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173174733cb0ea39f98fbe5396ed9397af8586ba","tid":778282,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"白紙一張最忌無人帶無人教<br />\n你估真係屌下就識咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"佢都有教既<br />\n不過佢真係太忙<br />\n同埋有啲野都唔係話一教就識家嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日叫我唔識問下師傅<br />\n初初入行蜜月期<br />\n我都仲有閒情逸致同啲師傅交流下<br />\n問下佢地啲野點解咁做點解咁溝<br />\n但依家自己真係忙到冇時間同冇心情問"},{"pid":"84fe26eb2e6aec2f3a9ae3c3fd71bc9208edc5fd","tid":778282,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"我上網睇科文要3-5年經驗<br />\n多數由落手落腳做既再轉"},{"pid":"6937eddf8531e31432a1650cf193d2077e9647c4","tid":778282,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"乜撚都唔識做科文?<br />\n發撚緊夢?"},{"pid":"33eb5b0f71877ae0da1db83e6b4a2942ea97e544","tid":778282,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fe26eb2e6aec2f3a9ae3c3fd71bc9208edc5fd","tid":778282,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:46:44.000Z","msg":"我上網睇科文要3-5年經驗<br />\n多數由落手落腳做既再轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/234909_f87bfb98dfda08cdbf0f47b2da9dd892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F234909_f87bfb98dfda08cdbf0f47b2da9dd892.png&h=a5c7b343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前幾個禮拜開會派既<br />\n右上=某公司科文要求<br />\n經驗浸浸下就識咖啦"},{"pid":"4472b538c80595ec96cbe8f3e017b4269836ae8e","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6937eddf8531e31432a1650cf193d2077e9647c4","tid":778282,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"乜撚都唔識做科文?<br />\n發撚緊夢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"我知嫁ching<br />\n要乜都識啲嘛<br />\n我都唔係話白𢭃人工果種人黎嫁<br />\n我都盡做<br />\n不過堅吃力<br />\n我依家就係知自己冇咁既料子冇咁既本事<br />\n諗緊點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f1ad536aa02049103b4aec84989f01b4639666","tid":778282,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"樓主讀咩出身? 定學師做上去?"},{"pid":"a29bb30060faaff769157f0e3c35bef8e0c9530a","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d4e6495540f785be1d76fef4ced22b3f24bed4","tid":778282,"uid":30701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"白紙坐正科文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"其實係Site Supervisor<br />\n其實係咪只係唔同叫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09b72ed78b9f4e03d0b5818b586285a0ec15df9","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f1ad536aa02049103b4aec84989f01b4639666","tid":778282,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"樓主讀咩出身? 定學師做上去?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"曾經係大樓地盤學師<br />\n讀...讀左個safety officer dip.<br />\n我知件事係錯晒嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574a846b65a68b80f9cf707cb841fb0a2bf9daad","tid":778282,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote