,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"裝修野入行都19K有冇搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a060d2fdb632490aa05a39b09e38af53cee3c9a0","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdf5dc302c89f057b655157897c097c9c17715cf","tid":778282,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"裝修野入行都19K有冇搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"我係咪應該好好珍惜"},{"pid":"7f37a7c165cbef4bcb7119e24e2fcca6da935fb3","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"9個正評<br />\n睇黎科文真係要識分身先做得黎<br />\n睇一個盤已經咁頭痛<br />\n睇幾個盤真係唔駛放假唔駛訓..<br />\n<br />\n咁site sup駛唔駛對客?"},{"pid":"5d9e4b9a95f38b1e496103f40545eec7a67861cd","tid":778282,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e618837b9e02bf1307e57951f66448ee168b69b4","tid":778282,"uid":200608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9e4b9a95f38b1e496103f40545eec7a67861cd","tid":778282,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"我以前都有咁既觀感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能人地背後做左好多準備功夫"},{"pid":"a562c675be12652ab32cac5c9bbd56616d8fffe4","tid":778282,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:06:42.000Z","msg":"大樓資源一定多過裝修<br />\n所以科文一定係大樓既遊"}]}